          "End of First Quarter",
          "Initial dataset coimprised 69116 students from the University of Washington, but majority class was undersampled in order to ensure that the dataset was balanced. \n\nNon-Completion was defined as did not complete program within 6 years after registering for the first-year. \n\nIn total, the model contained close to 1000 features",
          "Logistic Regression\nkNN\nRandom Forest\n",
          "10-Fold Cross-Validation",
          "{Accuracy: 0.6659 Logistic Regression, AUC: 0.729 - Logistic Regression}",
          "Authors also perform single-variable Logistic Regression to assess the predictive power of multiple features.\n\nWork also shows a following-level attempting to predict when a Dropout will happen.",
          "Curse of Dimensionality.\n\nLack of model optimization efforts.\n\nVery simple set of estimators used. "
        ]
